# Cloudflare Pages — short URLs and clean-URL handling
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Format: <source>  <destination>  [<status>]
# 301 = permanent redirect (default), 200 = rewrite (no URL change)

# NOTE on rules + Cloudflare Pages clean URLs:
# Cloudflare Pages serves /foo.html at /foo (clean URL) AND auto-redirects
# /foo.html → /foo with a 308. So a rule like "/foo /foo.html 301" creates a
# redirect loop with the clean URL system. Targets must be clean URLs.

